        &lt;/property&gt;
 3. Surround the column name with square brackets.

        &lt;property name=&quot;key&quot; type=&quot;string&quot;&gt;
            &lt;column name=&quot;[key]&quot; /&gt;
        &lt;/property&gt;

----------

